  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "Fix https://github.com/coder/internal/issues/826\r\n\r\nI wasn't able to recreate the flake, but my underlying assumption from reading the logs we have is that there is a race condition where the test will begin cleanup before the dev container recreation goroutine has a chance to call `devcontainer up`.\r\n\r\nI've refactored the test slightly and made it so that the test will not finish until either the context has timed out, or `Up` has been called.",
